children.value: I helped shape the culture of the company I worked at for 3 years. In this post I will detail how I did so, and why I did so.

Company culture is something that must be actively built and maintained.
A healthy, welcoming company culture is not something that simply happens because you're a nice person surrounded
by nice employees.
